title: IIM Mumbai Recruitment 2025 - Apply Online for 04 Management Trainee Posts
description: Indian Institute of Management Mumbai (IIM Mumbai) has declared the official notification for 2025. To fill up the vacancies for 04 Management Trainee Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the B.E/ B.Tech, M.E/ M.Tech, and M.Sc can grab this chance and apply for the IIM Mumbai Recruitment 2025 . The application process has started.
